   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ILO &#x2013; Unified Budget Results Accountability Framework (2018&#x2013;19) - Nigeria Country Project 19</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project strategy will comprise four complementary streams of work: Piggy back on existing meetings/events of employers and workers organizations; Tailored support to workplace programmes to scale up HIV testing and Social Health Protection sensitization; VCT initiatives in 7+1 States identified by NACA and UNAIDS as high burden states; World AIDS Day HIV Testing Events. As objectives, the project will: HIV testing approaches optimized, innovative approaches implemented and HIV testing and counselling services increased among women and men workers; and Strengthened HIV-sensitive social protection programmes for vulnerable workers.</narrative>
  </description>
